About this item

This Daily Chef 11-piece cookware set is made with heavy-gauge aluminum, features a PFOA-free  nonstick interior, durable porcelain enamel exterior in spice red, and is proudly Made in USA.

Description

This Daily Chef 11-piece Non-stick Cookware Set includes the following pieces to complete a multitude of everyday cooking tasks:  

  • 8” Saute Pan
  • 10” Saute Pan 
  • 4 qt. Covered Deep Saute Pan 
  • 2 qt. Covered Sauce Pan 
  • 3 qt. Covered Sauce Pan
  • 6 qt. Covered Stock Pot

Specifications

  • Heavy-gauge Aluminum Construction
  • Teflon Platinum High Performance PFOA Free Nonstick
  • Durable Porcelain Enameled Exterior Surface
  • Tempered Glass Lids
  • Soft-Grip Silicone Handles
  • Compatible with the Following Cooktops: Gas, Electric and Ceramic Glass
  • Oven-Safe up to 350ºF (176ºC)
  • Dishwasher-Safe
  • Made in USA
